1.0.name: wordpress/envato-affiliater
1.0.description:
Envato Affiliater Processes all content of Envato links and makes it possible to affiliate them. If you have found it then push your referral link, if already exists then change the username to your information.

Major new features in Envato Affiliater 1.2 includes: * Installs in seconds, takes even less time to configure! * Not only adds your own referral code to all links, but Envato Affiliater will also replace other peoples affiliate links with your own! In built Cloaking Support!  Easily hide your referral links using the bit.ly service! * Free updates!

PS: You wont need an [bitly API key]. if you leave it blank then the application will use public API.
